# Message API Endpoints
# This file contains HTTP requests for testing all message endpoints
# For detailed documentation about each endpoint's purpose and frontend usage,
# see the MESSAGE_API_DOCS.md file in this directory

### 1. Create a new message
# Purpose: Creates a new message in a conversation
# Frontend: Triggered when a user sends a new message in the chat interface
POST http://localhost:3000/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Hello, this is a test message",
  "sender_id": 1,
  "conversation_id": 1
}

### 2. Get all messages
# Purpose: Retrieves all messages in the system (admin functionality)
# Frontend: Admin dashboard for viewing all messages across the platform
GET http://localhost:3000/messages

### 3. Get a message by ID
# Purpose: Retrieves a specific message by its unique identifier
# Frontend: Loading a specific message when navigating directly to it
GET http://localhost:3000/messages/1

### 4. Get messages by user ID
# Purpose: Retrieves all messages sent by or received by a specific user
# Frontend: User's message history page or profile page
GET http://localhost:3000/messages/user/30

### 5. Get conversations for a user
# Purpose: Retrieves all conversations that a user is participating in
# Frontend: Main chat interface - conversation list in the sidebar
GET http://localhost:3000/messages/user/1/conversations

### 6. Get messages by conversation ID
# Purpose: Retrieves all messages within a specific conversation
# Frontend: Main chat window - displays the message history for the active conversation
GET http://localhost:3000/messages/conversation/1

### 7. Update a message
# Purpose: Updates an existing message (editing functionality)
# Frontend: When a user edits their message
PUT http://localhost:3000/messages/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Updated message content",
  "sender_id": 1,
  "conversation_id": 1
}

### 8. Delete a message
# Purpose: Deletes a message from the system
# Frontend: When a user deletes their message
DELETE http://localhost:3000/messages/1